      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled distinction. This specimen remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a commitment to absolute preservation. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, offering the aesthetic and mechanical integrity of a new machine. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
