    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014I've babied it since day one! It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
