      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a definitive example of automotive excellence, maintained to exacting standards. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated inline-six power plant with reinforced forged internals and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a close-ratio six-speed manual",
