      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero mechanical issues. Original paint and interior. No accidents. Clean title.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, while every technological feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history and an engine bay so clean it looks untouched. With incredibly low mileage and a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as a new car, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. No stone has been left unturned in maintaining this automotive masterpiece.",
      "price": 44900.0,
